  <div class="xhr_comment_body">
    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/143141404-cheese">CHeEse</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer16024852391476995622"><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23310699-crenshaw'>https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2...</a><br/><br/>It&apos;s a pretty simple, fast pace and rather short story that deals with serious topics. Of course you may find </span>
  <span id="freeText16024852391476995622" style="display:none"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23310699-crenshaw">https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2...</a><br /><br />It's a pretty simple, fast pace and rather short story that deals with serious topics. Of course you may find flaws or maybe not enjoy it as much as I do, but if you do like it, you might like Katherine Applegate's other stories, such as The One and Only Ivan and Wishtree. (Maybe the other 2 are better ha ha. Crenshaw just gave me a deeper impression after reading.)</span>
