        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer787014019" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2672719569366464949">It&apos;s not often I read a book that makes me forget I&apos;m a writer too. This one succeeded, madly. It stole hours of sleep. It wrapped me in cozy myth. It gave me the blessing of feeling like a kid again, snuggled up with a book, wondering how the hell 10pm became 4am. <br/><br/>Find. Buy. Consume. </span>
  <span id="freeText2672719569366464949" style="display:none">It's not often I read a book that makes me forget I'm a writer too. This one succeeded, madly. It stole hours of sleep. It wrapped me in cozy myth. It gave me the blessing of feeling like a kid again, snuggled up with a book, wondering how the hell 10pm became 4am. <br /><br />Find. Buy. Consume. </span>
